      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was looking at old photos today. it’s weird. i look at that person in the picture and i don't even recognize them. not just the face, but the spirit. it feels like that version of me actually died a long time ago. now i’m just... going through the motions. like i'm a ghost haunting my own life.",
