      "role": "user",
      "content": "reconnect? i don't think there's anything left to reconnect with. it's not like i'm just \"lost\" or \"going through a phase.\" it feels permanent. like the core of me—the part that actually felt alive and had purpose—is just gone. there's nothing underneath this shell but exhaustion. it feels like i'm just occupying space that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
