      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to believe that. all the advice i hear is about \"starting over\" or \"finding new meaning,\" but that requires a spark. that drive. i'm telling you, that person is dead. i feel like i'm just a walking corpse, performing the duties of a living person because i have to, but there's no soul in it. there's no light left. doesn't it just seem exhausting to keep pretending there's something there to save?",
